<https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/29887>
    dc:description "Figures 40 - 44. Scutopalus key illustrations. 40 a Coxae I-II faintly divided 40 b Coxae I-II totally divided 41 Coxae I-II fused medially 42 Dorsal shield with thick, rod-like setae present 43 Dorsal shield smooth or punctate 44 a Dorsal shield rugose 44 b Dorsal shield reticulate 44 c Dorsal shield sparsely granulate 45 a Setae mps, c 1, c 2, d 1, e 1, f 1 clavate 45 b Setae mps, c 1, c 2, d 1, e 1, f 1 setiform 46 Setae lps, mps, c 1, c 2, d 1, e 1, f 1 set on tubercles." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/29887" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

